95	
96	- Hero display: 0pt (set solid)
97	- Screen titles: -0.5pt (slight tightening for large type)
98	- Body text: 0.15pt (open, readable spacing)
99	- Caption and labels: 0.4pt (clear separation for small text)
100	
101	---
102	
103	## 4. Component Styles
104	
105	### Card
106	- **Corner radius:** 16 points
107	- **Shadow depth:** Soft, diffused shadow — 8 points blur, 2 points offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) in light mode; rgba(0,0,0,0.25) in dark mode. The shadow feels like gentle morning light creating a soft pool beneath the card.
108	- **Background:** Morning Mist (#FAFAFA) in light mode; Deep Twilight (#1E1B2E) in dark mode
109	- **Internal padding:** 16 points all sides; 20 points for cards containing action buttons
110	- **Tap feedback:** Subtle scale-down to 98% on press, with 200ms ease-out return. The press feels like a gentle press into a soft surface rather than a click.
111	- **Spacing between cards:** 12 points
112	
113	### Buttons
114	
115	**Primary Button**
116	- Shape: Pill-shaped (fully rounded on all corners, corner radius equals half the button height)
117	- Minimum height: 48 points (touch target compliance)
118	- Background: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
119	- Text: White (#FFFFFF), SemiBold, 14pt
120	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 95%, background darkens by 8% brightness
121	- Corner radius: 24 points (fully rounded pill)
122	
123	**Secondary Button**
124	- Shape: Pill-shaped
125	- Minimum height: 48 points
126	- Background: Transparent with Lavender Bloom border (2 points stroke) in light mode; Transparent with Twilight Bloom border in dark mode
127	- Text: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
128	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 95%, background fills with 10% primary color
129	- Corner radius: 24 points
130	
131	**Text Button**
132	- Shape: No background, no border
133	- Minimum height: 48 points
134	- Text: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Text button inherits no background, only color
135	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out opacity reduction to 60%
136	
137	**FAB (Floating Action Button)**
138	- Size: 56 points diameter
139	- Background: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED); Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
140	- Icon: White, 24 points
141	- Shadow: Medium diffused shadow, 12 points blur
142	- Press feedback: 200ms scale to 90%, shadow intensifies slightly
143	
144	### Text Input
145	- **Decoration style:** Filled background — a rounded container that feels like a gentle trough for text
146	- **Corner radius:** 12 points
147	- **Fill color:** Stone 100 (#F5F5F4) in light mode; Night Stone 100 (#2D2B3A) in dark mode
148	- **Border:** None at rest; on focus, a 2-point Lavender Bloom border appears with smooth 200ms transition
149	- **Label behavior:** Floating label that rises above the field on focus or when content is present; label color transitions from Stone 400 (#A8A29E) to Lavender Bloom on focus
150	- **Error state:** Border becomes Soft Coral (#EF4444), error message appears below in Soft Coral, 14pt
151	- **Minimum height:** 56 points to ensure comfortable touch interaction
152	
153	### Chip
154	- **Shape:** Fully rounded pill (corner radius = half the chip height)
155	- **Corner radius:** 16 points (pill shape)
156	- **Background (default):** Stone 100 (#F5F5F4) in light mode; Night Stone 100 (#2D2B3A) in dark mode
157	- **Background (selected):** Lavender Bloom at 15% opacity (#7C3AED1A), with Lavender Bloom text
158	- **Minimum height:** 32 points (comfortable touch target)
159	- **Horizontal padding:** 12 points left and right
160	- **Tap feedback:** 150ms opacity shift to selected state, no scale change (chips feel like gentle toggles, not buttons)
161	
162	### Bottom Sheet
163	- **Top corner radius:** 28 points — large, prominent rounding that feels organic and soft
164	- **Background:** Warm White (#FFFFFF) in light mode; Charcoal Surface (#252336) in dark mode
165	- **Handle bar:** 40 points wide, 4 points tall, centered at top, Stone 300 (#D6D3D1) color in light mode; Night Stone 200 in dark mode. The handle feels like a gentle grip point, not structural.
166	- **Maximum height:** 90% of screen height for full sheets; 50% for half sheets
167	- **Shadow:** Soft diffused shadow, 16 points blur, 4 points offset-y
168	- **Open animation:** 250ms smooth deceleration — slides up from bottom edge with subtle fade
169	
170	### Navigation Bar (Bottom Tabs)
171	- **Background color:** Warm White (#FFFFFF) in light mode; Charcoal Surface (#252336) in dark mode
172	- **Active indicator:** A small rounded pill beneath the active tab icon and label. The pill is filled with Lavender Bloom at 15% opacity. The indicator transitions smoothly (200ms) between tabs.
173	- **Icon style:** Outlined icons for inactive state, filled icons for active state — the active tab is visually "filled" with color
174	- **Icon size:** 24 points
175	- **Label visibility:** Labels are always visible below icons — no hidden label behavior. Text is SemiBold 11pt when active, Regular 11pt when inactive.
176	- **Touch target:** Each tab item has a minimum 48-point touch target height
177	- **Safe area:** Bottom navigation respects the home indicator area on notched devices
178	
179	### App Bar
180	- **Background:** Transparent to scaffold background color (Lavender Tint #F5F3FF in light mode; Night Sky #13111C in dark mode). The AppBar feels like it floats over the content.
181	- **Title text style:** SemiBold 20pt, Deep Graphite (#1F2937) in light mode; Soft Pearl (#F3F4F6) in dark mode
182	- **Scroll behavior:** On scrollable content, the AppBar has a subtle fade-in effect as content scrolls beneath it. On screens with SliverAppBar, the AppBar collapses to show a smaller representation.
183	- **Leading/back button:** Icon button with 48-point touch target, Lavender Bloom on tap
184	
185	---
186	
187	## 5. Layout Principles
188	
189	- **Base spacing unit:** 8 points — all spacing is derived from multiples of 8
190	- **Screen horizontal padding:** 16 points from each edge
191	- **Section vertical spacing:** 24 points between major sections
192	- **Card internal padding:** 16 points all sides
193	- **Card gap:** 12 points between cards in a grid or list
194	- **List item minimum height:** 56 points (comfortable touch target for interactive list items)
195	- **Minimum touch target:** 48 points (compliant with mobile accessibility standards)
196	- **Bottom sheet handle bar:** 40 points wide, 4 points tall, centered 20 points from top
197	- **Safe area awareness:** Respect status bar at top (add 12 points padding when status bar is visible) and home indicator at bottom (bottom navigation and FAB account for this)
198	- **Grid gutters:** 12 points between columns in 2-column grids
199	- **Card corner radius:** 16 points for standard cards; 12 points for smaller card variants
200	
201	---
202	
203	## 6. Motion & Animation
204	
205	Motion is gentle, purposeful, and never jarring. The app feels like a calm, flowing experience rather than a reactive, mechanical one.
206	
207	- **Page transitions:** 300ms duration, smooth deceleration. Screen content slides and fades simultaneously — the new screen appears to gently settle into place.
208	- **Micro-interactions:** 200ms duration, snappy ease-out. Button presses, chip selections, toggle switches — responses feel quick but soft, like a gentle tap on a responsive surface.
209	- **Hero transitions:** 350ms duration, fast-out-slow-in easing. When navigating from a list to a detail view (e.g., article reader), shared elements like images and titles smoothly expand and continue their motion arc.
210	- **Staggered list reveals:** 50ms delay between each item. When content loads, list items cascade into view in a waterfall — items appear 50ms apart, creating a sense of gentle unfolding rather than a sudden dump of content.
211	- **Bottom sheets:** 250ms duration, smooth deceleration. Sheets slide up from the bottom edge, decelerating naturally as they reach their resting position.
212	- **Pull-to-refresh:** 150ms duration, quick snap. The refresh indicator appears and dismisses quickly but not abruptly.
213	- **Tab indicator movement:** 200ms duration, ease-in-out. The active indicator pill smoothly glides between tab positions.
214	- **Card tap feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return to 100%.
215	- **FAB appearance:** 200ms fade-in with subtle scale from 95% to 100%.
216	
217	---
218	
219	## 7. Anti-Patterns (Banned Design Rules)
220	
221	- No default platform colors — every color comes from the design system palette
222	- No ad-hoc text sizing — all text uses the defined type scale
223	- No inconsistent spacing — all spacing uses the 8-point base unit scale
224	- No arbitrary elevation — every shadow level communicates a specific hierarchy
225	- No Inter or Roboto — Nunito is the only font family
226	- No purple or neon AI aesthetic — colors are warm pastels, not synthetic
227	- No generic gradients — backgrounds are flat or subtly tinted, not gradient-washed
228	- No shadows without purpose — elevation always communicates hierarchy
229	- No desktop patterns — no sidebars, hover tooltips, right-click menus, or desktop-only interaction patterns
230	- No touch targets smaller than 48 points
231	- No critical actions outside the thumb zone (bottom two-thirds of screen height)
232	- No pure black (#000000) anywhere — deep charcoal and off-black only
233	- No pure white (#FFFFFF) for text — use off-white tones that reduce eye strain
[2026-05-19T01:09:55.860Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_chy8cjeh72wo_2","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump — UX Specification\n2\t\n3\t## Part 1: Project Overview\n4\t\n5\t**App Name:** Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump\n6\t**Platform:** Flutter Mobile (iOS & Android)\n7\t**Core Identity:** Calming, nurturing, empowering, trustworthy\n8\t\n9\t### User Personas\n10\t\n11\t| Persona | Description | Key Goals |\n12\t|---|---|---|\n13\t| First-Time Expecting Mothers | First pregnancy, seeking guidance and reassurance | Week-by-week progress, trusted information, due date tracking |\n14\t| Health-Conscious Mothers | Actively monitors weight, nutrition, exercise | Data-driven charts, daily logs, actionable insights |\n15\t| Anxiety-Prone Mothers | Elevated stress and emotional changes | Breathing exercises, mood logging, stress relief |\n16\t\n17\t---\n18\t\n19\t## Part 2: Vibe\n20\t\n21\t- **Visual Atmosphere:** Soft, warm nursery aesthetic — like a cozy sunlit room with gentle natural light\n22\t- **Color Mood:** Cool-warm pastels anchored by lavender with blush rose accents; serene, never clinical\n23\t- **Typography Character:** Rounded, friendly, modern — Google Fonts \"Nunito\" family; generous letter-spacing for calm readability\n24\t- **Motion Personality:** Gentle spring-based animations with `Curves.easeInOut`; 300–400ms standard duration; nothing abrupt or bouncy\n25\t\n26\t---\n27\t\n28\t## Part 3: Screens\n29\t\n30\t### 3.1 Home (`/`)\n31\t\n32\t**Purpose:** Central dashboard showing today's snapshot — pregnancy progress, quick-log buttons, and personalized wellness nudges.\n33\t\n34\t**Scaffold:**\n35\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Baby Bump\", no back button, trailing avatar icon\n36\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Visible (4 tabs)\n37\t- `FAB`: None\n38\t\n39\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing, shows current week badge).\n40\t\n41\t**Sections:**\n42\t1. **Week Banner** — Large centered card showing pregnancy week, due date countdown, fruit-size comparison\n43\t2. **Mood Check-In Card** — Quick mood selector (5 emojis), tappable to log\n44\t3. **Today's Checklist** — Horizontal scrollable chips: weight entry, water intake, mood, symptom log\n45\t4. **Quick Actions** — 4 primary buttons: Log Weight, Log Mood, Log Symptoms, View Education\n46\t5. **Weekly Tip** — Single card with rotating wellness tip\n47\t\n48\t**Data:** Reads from `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date), `MoodEntryProvider` (today's mood), `SelfCareCheckState` (today's checklist)\n49\t\n50\t**Interactions:** Tap mood → log mood; tap weight → push weight form; tap symptom → push symptom form; tap education → tab to Education\n51\t\n52\t**Transitions:** Arrives via bottom nav tab (no animation); pull-down refreshes widget data.\n53\t\n54\t---\n55\t\n56\t### 3.2 Cycle Tracking (`/cycle-tracking`)\n57\t\n58\t**Purpose:** Log menstrual cycles, view ovulation predictions, manage cycle-related reminders.\n59\t\n60\t**Scaffold:**\n61\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Cycle Tracking\", back button\n62\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n63\t- `FAB`: `+` to log a new cycle entry\n64\t\n65\t**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n66\t\n67\t**Sections:**\n68\t1. **Current Cycle Card** — Shows days since last period, next ovulation window estimate\n69\t2. **Cycle History List** — Chronological list of logged cycles with length indicators\n70\t\n71\t**Data:** `CycleEntryProvider`\n72\t\n73\t**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet form for new cycle log; long-press history entry → edit/delete sheet; tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet\n74\t\n75\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav Browse; swipe-back to dismiss.\n76\t\n77\t---\n78\t\n79\t### 3.3 Weight & Nutrition (`/weight-nutrition`)\n80\t\n81\t**Purpose:** Log daily weight, view progress chart, read stage-specific nutrition tips.\n82\t\n83\t**Scaffold:**\n84\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Weight & Nutrition\", back button\n85\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n86\t- `FAB`: `+` to log today's weight\n87\t\n88\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n89\t\n90\t**Sections:**\n91\t1. **Progress Chart** — Line chart of weight over time; toggles 1 week / 1 month / all time\n92\t2. **Latest Entry** — Today's weight with delta from previous entry\n93\t3. **Nutrition Tips** — Stage-specific card (updates based on current pregnancy week)\n94\t4. **Weight Log List** — Scrollable list of all entries (date + weight + optional note)\n95\t\n96\t**Data:** `WeightEntryProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider` (for week-based tips)\n97\t\n98\t**Interactions:** Tap chart toggle → re-renders chart; tap `+` → bottom sheet form; long-press log entry → edit/delete sheet; tap nutrition tip → expand detail\n99\t\n100\t**Transitions:** Push from Home Browse tab or Education detail; swipe-back to dismiss.\n101\t\n102\t---\n103\t\n104\t### 3.4 Pregnancy Progress (`/pregnancy-progress`)\n105\t\n106\t**Purpose:** Due date management, week-by-week body change descriptions, fetal development visuals.\n107\t\n108\t**Scaffold:**\n109\t- `AppBar`: Title \"My Pregnancy\", back button\n110\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n111\t- `FAB`: None\n112\t\n113\t**Body:** `PageView` with `PageController` (week-by-week swiper) + bottom summary section.\n114\t\n115\t**Sections:**\n116\t1. **Week Hero** — Full-screen illustrated card with fruit-size comparison and week number prominently displayed\n117\t2. **Body Changes** — Bulleted list of what to expect this week\n118\t3. **Baby Development** — Short paragraph on fetal development\n119\t4. **Self-Care Tips** — 3 actionable tips for this week\n120\t5. **Due Date Summary** — Bottom card showing due date, days remaining, trimester badge\n121\t\n122\t**Data:** `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date)\n123\t\n124\t**Interactions:** Swipe left/right → navigate weeks; tap self-care tip → expand to full recommendation\n125\t\n126\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; PageView swipe-back returns to previous screen.\n127\t\n128\t---\n129\t\n130\t### 3.5 Mindfulness (`/mindfulness`)\n131\t\n132\t**Purpose:** Guided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, mindful activity suggestions.\n133\t\n134\t**Scaffold:**\n135\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button\n136\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n137\t- `FAB`: None\n138\t\n139\t**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n140\t\n141\t**Sections:**\n142\t1. **Breathing Exercises** — Card list with exercise name, duration, difficulty badge; tap → full-screen breathing animation overlay\n143\t2. **Stretching & Self-Care** — Card list with routine name, trimester suitability, estimated time; tap → step-by-step guide bottom sheet\n144\t\n145\t**Data:** Static exercise catalog (no provider dependency for MVP); `SelfCareCheckState` for completion tracking\n146\t\n147\t**Interactions:** Tap breathing card → overlay:breathing-exercise (full-screen animated overlay); tap stretching card → overlay:stretching-guide (bottom sheet with steps)\n148\t\n149\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav; overlay slides up from bottom.\n150\t\n151\t---\n152\t\n153\t### 3.6 Health Log (`/health-log`)\n154\t\n155\t**Purpose:** Unified timeline of all health entries — symptoms, doctor visits, reminders.\n156\t\n157\t**Scaffold:**\n158\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Health Log\", back button, trailing filter icon\n159\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n160\t- `FAB`: `+` to add new entry\n161\t\n162\t**Body:** `ListView` with chronological timeline.\n163\t\n164\t**Sections:**\n165\t1. **Timeline** — Mixed list of `SymptomEntry`, `DoctorVisit`, `Reminder` entries sorted by date descending\n166\t2. **Summary Stats** — Top banner: total symptoms logged this week, next upcoming reminder\n167\t\n168\t**Data:** `SymptomEntryProvider`, `DoctorVisitProvider`, `ReminderProvider`\n169\t\n170\t**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet with entry type selector; tap entry → detail/edit bottom sheet; tap filter icon → bottom sheet filter options\n171\t\n172\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n173\t\n174\t---\n175\t\n176\t### 3.7 Mood & Wellness (`/mood-wellness`)\n177\t\n178\t**Purpose:** Log daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over time, receive gentle wellness nudges.\n179\t\n180\t**Scaffold:**\n181\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mood & Wellness\", back button\n182\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n183\t- `FAB`: None\n184\t\n185\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n186\t\n187\t**Sections:**\n188\t1. **Today's Mood Card** — Large emoji selector (5 options) + optional note field; tap to log\n189\t2. **Mood Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of mood scores; tap data point → day detail\n190\t3. **Energy Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of energy levels\n191\t4. **Wellness Tip** — Contextual recommendation based on recent mood/energy patterns\n192\t\n193\t**Data:** `MoodEntryProvider`\n194\t\n195\t**Interactions:** Tap emoji → saves mood for today; tap chart point → bottom sheet with day's detail; tap wellness tip → expand\n196\t\n197\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n198\t\n199\t---\n200\t\n201\t### 3.8 Education (`/education`)\n202\t\n203\t**Purpose:** Browse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic.\n204\t\n205\t**Scaffold:**\n206\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon\n207\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n208\t- `FAB`: None\n209\t\n210\t**Body:** `ListView` with topic sections.\n211\t\n212\t**Sections:**\n213\t1. **Featured Article** — Hero card at top with large image and headline\n214\t2. **Topics Grid** — 2-column grid of topic cards: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health\n215\t3. **Recent Articles** — Horizontal scroll of recently viewed articles\n216\t\n217\t**Data:** Static article catalog (no provider for MVP); `ArticleProvider` for bookmarking\n218\t\n219\t**Interactions:** Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list); tap article → `/article-reader/:id`; tap search → search overlay; tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark\n220\t\n221\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or Browse tab; swipe-back to dismiss.\n222\t\n223\t---\n224\t\n225\t### 3.9 Article Reader (`/article-reader/:id`)\n226\t\n227\t**Purpose:** Read a single article with clean typography, bookmark capability.\n228\t\n229\t**Scaffold:**\n230\t- `AppBar`: Title from article topic, back button, trailing bookmark and share icons\n231\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n232\t- `FAB`: None\n233\t\n234\t**Body:** `SingleChildScrollView` with article content.\n235\t\n236\t**Sections:**\n237\t1. **Article Header** — Hero image, topic badge, title, read-time estimate\n238\t2. **Article Body** — Formatted text with section headers, pull-quote styling\n239\t3. **Related Articles** — Bottom section with 2–3 related article cards\n240\t\n241\t**Data:** `ArticleProvider`\n242\t\n243\t**Interactions:** Tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark state; tap share → system share sheet; tap related article → push new Article Reader; scroll → collapses header image\n244\t\n245\t**Transitions:** Push from Education list or Home; shared-element hero from article card; swipe-back to dismiss.\n246\t\n247\t---\n248\t\n249\t### 3.10 Settings (`/settings`)\n250\t\n251\t**Purpose:** Manage user profile, due date, notification preferences, and data export.\n252\t\n253\t**Scaffold:**\n254\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Settings\", back button\n255\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n256\t- `FAB`: None\n257\t\n258\t**Body:** `ListView` grouped into preference sections.\n259\t\n260\t**Sections:**\n261\t1. **Profile** — Due date display with edit capability, name field\n262\t2. **Notifications** — Toggle switches for reminder categories\n263\t3. **Data** — Export data button, clear data button (with confirmation dialog)\n264\t4. **About** — App version, privacy policy link\n265\t\n266\t**Data:** `UserPreferencesProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n267\t\n268\t**Interactions:** Tap due date → date picker bottom sheet; tap export → generates shareable file; tap clear data → confirmation dialog\n269\t\n270\t**Transitions:** Push from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar; swipe-back to dismiss.\n271\t\n272\t---\n273\t\n274\t## Part 4: Navigation Architecture\n275\t\n276\t### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)\n277\t```\n278\tShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)\n279\t├── Home (/')\n280\t├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition\n281\t├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log\n282\t└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness\n283\t```\n284\t\n285\t### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)\n286\t| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |\n287\t|---|---|---|---|\n288\t| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |\n289\t| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |\n290\t| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |\n291\t| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |\n292\t\n293\t### Push Routes (detail screens)\n294\t| Screen | Route | Parent |\n295\t|---|---|---|\n296\t| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |\n297\t| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |\n298\t| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |\n299\t| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |\n300\t| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |\n301\t| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |\n302\t| Education | `/education` | Library tab |\n303\t| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |\n304\t| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |\n305\t\n306\t### Modal Overlays\n307\t| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |\n308\t|---|---|---|---|\n309\t| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |\n310\t| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |\n311\t| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |\n312\t| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |\n313\t\n314\t### Deep Links\n315\t- `babybump://home` → `/`\n316\t- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`\n317\t- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`\n318\t- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`\n319\t\n320\t---\n321\t\n322\t## Part 5: Data Context\n323\t\n324\t### Entities\n325\t\n326\t| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |\n327\t|---|---|---|---|\n328\t| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |\n329\t| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |\n330\t| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |\n331\t| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |\n332\t| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |\n333\t| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |\n334\t| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |\n335\t| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |\n336\t| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |\n337\t| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |\n338\t\n339\t### Relationships\n340\t- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)\n341\t- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts\n342\t- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard\n343\t- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab\n344\t\n345\t---\n346\t\n347\t## Part 6: Design Tokens\n348\t\n349\t### Color Palette (Material 3 — Lavender Seed)\n350\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n351\t|---|---|---|\n352\t| `seed` | `#A78BFA` | Primary color seed (soft violet) |\n353\t| `primary` | `#7C3AED` | AppBar, FAB, primary actions |\n354\t| `secondary` | `#F9A8D4` | Blush rose accents, mood emojis |\n355\t| `tertiary` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, checkmarks |\n356\t| `surface` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n357\t| `background` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background (lavender tint) |\n358\t| `error` | `#EF4444` | Validation errors, delete actions |\n359\t| `onPrimary` | `#FFFFFF` | Text on primary color |\n360\t| `onSurface` | `#1F2937` | Body text |\n361\t| `onSurfaceVariant` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n362\t\n363\t### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n364\t| Style | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height |\n365\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n366\t| `displayLarge` | Nunito | 32sp | 700 | 40sp |\n367\t| `headlineMedium` | Nunito | 24sp | 700 | 32sp |\n368\t| `titleLarge` | Nunito | 20sp | 600 | 28sp |\n369\t| `titleMedium` | Nunito | 16sp | 600 | 24sp |\n370\t| `bodyLarge` | Nunito | 16sp | 400 | 24sp |\n371\t| `bodyMedium` | Nunito | 14sp | 400 | 20sp |\n372\t| `labelLarge` | Nunito | 14sp | 600 | 20sp |\n373\t| `caption` | Nunito | 12sp | 400 | 16sp |\n374\t\n375\t### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n376\t| Token | Value |\n377\t|---|---|\n378\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n379\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n380\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n381\t| `md` | 16dp |\n382\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n383\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n384\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n385\t\n386\t### Corner Radius Scale\n387\t| Token | Value |\n388\t|---|---|\n389\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips, small cards) |\n390\t| `md` | 12dp (cards, bottom sheets) |\n391\t| `lg` | 16dp (large cards, dialogs) |\n392\t| `full` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n393\t\n394\t### Elevation (Material 3 Tonal)\n395\t| Token | Usage |\n396\t|---|---|\n397\t| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n398\t| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n399\t| `level2` | FAB, BottomSheet |\n400\t| `level3` | Dialogs, overlays |\n401\t\n402\t### Motion\n403\t| Token | Value |\n404\t|---|---|\n405\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n406\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n407\t| `durationLong` | 400ms |\n408\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n409\t| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n410\t| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n411\t| `sharedAxis` | Hero transitions between list and detail |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2444bea1-bf77-4458-b4d2-72e2e3e7f792","uuid":"f97c2d3c-2e68-4d9e-9d63-a194cfb401ad","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:09:55.860Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/UX.md","content":"# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump — UX Specification\n\n## Part 1: Project Overview\n\n**App Name:** Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump\n**Platform:** Flutter Mobile (iOS & Android)\n**Core Identity:** Calming, nurturing, empowering, trustworthy\n\n### User Personas\n\n| Persona | Description | Key Goals |\n|---|---|---|\n| First-Time Expecting Mothers | First pregnancy, seeking guidance and reassurance | Week-by-week progress, trusted information, due date tracking |\n| Health-Conscious Mothers | Actively monitors weight, nutrition, exercise | Data-driven charts, daily logs, actionable insights |\n| Anxiety-Prone Mothers | Elevated stress and emotional changes | Breathing exercises, mood logging, stress relief |\n\n---\n\n## Part 2: Vibe\n\n- **Visual Atmosphere:** Soft, warm nursery aesthetic — like a cozy sunlit room with gentle natural light\n- **Color Mood:** Cool-warm pastels anchored by lavender with blush rose accents; serene, never clinical\n- **Typography Character:** Rounded, friendly, modern — Google Fonts \"Nunito\" family; generous letter-spacing for calm readability\n- **Motion Personality:** Gentle spring-based animations with `Curves.easeInOut`; 300–400ms standard duration; nothing abrupt or bouncy\n\n---\n\n## Part 3: Screens\n\n### 3.1 Home (`/`)\n\n**Purpose:** Central dashboard showing today's snapshot — pregnancy progress, quick-log buttons, and personalized wellness nudges.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Baby Bump\", no back button, trailing avatar icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Visible (4 tabs)\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing, shows current week badge).\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Week Banner** — Large centered card showing pregnancy week, due date countdown, fruit-size comparison\n2. **Mood Check-In Card** — Quick mood selector (5 emojis), tappable to log\n3. **Today's Checklist** — Horizontal scrollable chips: weight entry, water intake, mood, symptom log\n4. **Quick Actions** — 4 primary buttons: Log Weight, Log Mood, Log Symptoms, View Education\n5. **Weekly Tip** — Single card with rotating wellness tip\n\n**Data:** Reads from `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date), `MoodEntryProvider` (today's mood), `SelfCareCheckState` (today's checklist)\n\n**Interactions:** Tap mood → log mood; tap weight → push weight form; tap symptom → push symptom form; tap education → tab to Education\n\n**Transitions:** Arrives via bottom nav tab (no animation); pull-down refreshes widget data.\n\n---\n\n### 3.2 Cycle Tracking (`/cycle-tracking`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log menstrual cycles, view ovulation predictions, manage cycle-related reminders.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Cycle Tracking\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to log a new cycle entry\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Current Cycle Card** — Shows days since last period, next ovulation window estimate\n2. **Cycle History List** — Chronological list of logged cycles with length indicators\n\n**Data:** `CycleEntryProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet form for new cycle log; long-press history entry → edit/delete sheet; tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav Browse; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 Weight & Nutrition (`/weight-nutrition`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log daily weight, view progress chart, read stage-specific nutrition tips.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Weight & Nutrition\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to log today's weight\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Progress Chart** — Line chart of weight over time; toggles 1 week / 1 month / all time\n2. **Latest Entry** — Today's weight with delta from previous entry\n3. **Nutrition Tips** — Stage-specific card (updates based on current pregnancy week)\n4. **Weight Log List** — Scrollable list of all entries (date + weight + optional note)\n\n**Data:** `WeightEntryProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider` (for week-based tips)\n\n**Interactions:** Tap chart toggle → re-renders chart; tap `+` → bottom sheet form; long-press log entry → edit/delete sheet; tap nutrition tip → expand detail\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home Browse tab or Education detail; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.4 Pregnancy Progress (`/pregnancy-progress`)\n\n**Purpose:** Due date management, week-by-week body change descriptions, fetal development visuals.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"My Pregnancy\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `PageView` with `PageController` (week-by-week swiper) + bottom summary section.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Week Hero** — Full-screen illustrated card with fruit-size comparison and week number prominently displayed\n2. **Body Changes** — Bulleted list of what to expect this week\n3. **Baby Development** — Short paragraph on fetal development\n4. **Self-Care Tips** — 3 actionable tips for this week\n5. **Due Date Summary** — Bottom card showing due date, days remaining, trimester badge\n\n**Data:** `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date)\n\n**Interactions:** Swipe left/right → navigate weeks; tap self-care tip → expand to full recommendation\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; PageView swipe-back returns to previous screen.\n\n---\n\n### 3.5 Mindfulness (`/mindfulness`)\n\n**Purpose:** Guided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, mindful activity suggestions.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Breathing Exercises** — Card list with exercise name, duration, difficulty badge; tap → full-screen breathing animation overlay\n2. **Stretching & Self-Care** — Card list with routine name, trimester suitability, estimated time; tap → step-by-step guide bottom sheet\n\n**Data:** Static exercise catalog (no provider dependency for MVP); `SelfCareCheckState` for completion tracking\n\n**Interactions:** Tap breathing card → overlay:breathing-exercise (full-screen animated overlay); tap stretching card → overlay:stretching-guide (bottom sheet with steps)\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav; overlay slides up from bottom.\n\n---\n\n### 3.6 Health Log (`/health-log`)\n\n**Purpose:** Unified timeline of all health entries — symptoms, doctor visits, reminders.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Health Log\", back button, trailing filter icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to add new entry\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with chronological timeline.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Timeline** — Mixed list of `SymptomEntry`, `DoctorVisit`, `Reminder` entries sorted by date descending\n2. **Summary Stats** — Top banner: total symptoms logged this week, next upcoming reminder\n\n**Data:** `SymptomEntryProvider`, `DoctorVisitProvider`, `ReminderProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet with entry type selector; tap entry → detail/edit bottom sheet; tap filter icon → bottom sheet filter options\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.7 Mood & Wellness (`/mood-wellness`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over time, receive gentle wellness nudges.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Mood & Wellness\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Today's Mood Card** — Large emoji selector (5 options) + optional note field; tap to log\n2. **Mood Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of mood scores; tap data point → day detail\n3. **Energy Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of energy levels\n4. **Wellness Tip** — Contextual recommendation based on recent mood/energy patterns\n\n**Data:** `MoodEntryProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap emoji → saves mood for today; tap chart point → bottom sheet with day's detail; tap wellness tip → expand\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.8 Education (`/education`)\n\n**Purpose:** Browse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with topic sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Featured Article** — Hero card at top with large image and headline\n2. **Topics Grid** — 2-column grid of topic cards: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health\n3. **Recent Articles** — Horizontal scroll of recently viewed articles\n\n**Data:** Static article catalog (no provider for MVP); `ArticleProvider` for bookmarking\n\n**Interactions:** Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list); tap article → `/article-reader/:id`; tap search → search overlay; tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or Browse tab; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.9 Article Reader (`/article-reader/:id`)\n\n**Purpose:** Read a single article with clean typography, bookmark capability.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title from article topic, back button, trailing bookmark and share icons\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `SingleChildScrollView` with article content.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Article Header** — Hero image, topic badge, title, read-time estimate\n2. **Article Body** — Formatted text with section headers, pull-quote styling\n3. **Related Articles** — Bottom section with 2–3 related article cards\n\n**Data:** `ArticleProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark state; tap share → system share sheet; tap related article → push new Article Reader; scroll → collapses header image\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Education list or Home; shared-element hero from article card; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.10 Settings (`/settings`)\n\n**Purpose:** Manage user profile, due date, notification preferences, and data export.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Settings\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` grouped into preference sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Profile** — Due date display with edit capability, name field\n2. **Notifications** — Toggle switches for reminder categories\n3. **Data** — Export data button, clear data button (with confirmation dialog)\n4. **About** — App version, privacy policy link\n\n**Data:** `UserPreferencesProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap due date → date picker bottom sheet; tap export → generates shareable file; tap clear data → confirmation dialog\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n## Part 4: Navigation Architecture\n\n### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)\n```\nShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)\n├── Home (/')\n├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition\n├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log\n└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness\n```\n\n### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)\n| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |\n| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |\n| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |\n| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |\n\n### Push Routes (detail screens)\n| Screen | Route | Parent |\n|---|---|---|\n| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |\n| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |\n| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |\n| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |\n| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |\n| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |\n| Education | `/education` | Library tab |\n| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |\n| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |\n\n### Modal Overlays\n| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |\n| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |\n| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |\n| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |\n\n### Deep Links\n- `babybump://home` → `/`\n- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`\n- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`\n- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`\n\n---\n\n## Part 5: Data Context\n\n### Entities\n\n| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |\n| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |\n| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |\n| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |\n| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |\n| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |\n| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |\n| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |\n| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |\n| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |\n\n### Relationships\n- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)\n- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts\n- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard\n- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab\n\n---\n\n## Part 6: Design Tokens\n\n### Color Palette (Material 3 — Lavender Seed)\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `seed` | `#A78BFA` | Primary color seed (soft violet) |\n| `primary` | `#7C3AED` | AppBar, FAB, primary actions |\n| `secondary` | `#F9A8D4` | Blush rose accents, mood emojis |\n| `tertiary` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, checkmarks |\n| `surface` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `background` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background (lavender tint) |\n| `error` | `#EF4444` | Validation errors, delete actions |\n| `onPrimary` | `#FFFFFF` | Text on primary color |\n| `onSurface` | `#1F2937` | Body text |\n| `onSurfaceVariant` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n\n### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n| Style | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | Nunito | 32sp | 700 | 40sp |\n| `headlineMedium` | Nunito | 24sp | 700 | 32sp |\n| `titleLarge` | Nunito | 20sp | 600 | 28sp |\n| `titleMedium` | Nunito | 16sp | 600 | 24sp |\n| `bodyLarge` | Nunito | 16sp | 400 | 24sp |\n| `bodyMedium` | Nunito | 14sp | 400 | 20sp |\n| `labelLarge` | Nunito | 14sp | 600 | 20sp |\n| `caption` | Nunito | 12sp | 400 | 16sp |\n\n### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius Scale\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips, small cards) |\n| `md` | 12dp (cards, bottom sheets) |\n| `lg` | 16dp (large cards, dialogs) |\n| `full` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n\n### Elevation (Material 3 Tonal)\n| Token | Usage |\n|---|---|\n| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n| `level2` | FAB, BottomSheet |\n| `level3` | Dialogs, overlays |\n\n### Motion\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n| `durationLong` | 400ms |\n| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n| `sharedAxis` | Hero transitions between list and detail |","numLines":411,"startLine":1,"totalLines":411}}}
[2026-05-19T01:09:55.861Z] [STREAM_EVENT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_chy8cjeh72wo_2","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump — UX Specification\n2\t\n3\t## Part 1: Project Overview\n4\t\n5\t**App Name:** Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump\n6\t**Platform:** Flutter Mobile (iOS & Android)\n7\t**Core Identity:** Calming, nurturing, empowering, trustworthy\n8\t\n9\t### User Personas\n10\t\n11\t| Persona | Description | Key Goals |\n12\t|---|---|---|\n13\t| First-Time Expecting Mothers | First pregnancy, seeking guidance and reassurance | Week-by-week progress, trusted information, due date tracking |\n14\t| Health-Conscious Mothers | Actively monitors weight, nutrition, exercise | Data-driven charts, daily logs, actionable insights |\n15\t| Anxiety-Prone Mothers | Elevated stress and emotional changes | Breathing exercises, mood logging, stress relief |\n16\t\n17\t---\n18\t\n19\t## Part 2: Vibe\n20\t\n21\t- **Visual Atmosphere:** Soft, warm nursery aesthetic — like a cozy sunlit room with gentle natural light\n22\t- **Color Mood:** Cool-warm pastels anchored by lavender with blush rose accents; serene, never clinical\n23\t- **Typography Character:** Rounded, friendly, modern — Google Fonts \"Nunito\" family; generous letter-spacing for calm readability\n24\t- **Motion Personality:** Gentle spring-based animations with `Curves.easeInOut`; 300–400ms standard duration; nothing abrupt or bouncy\n25\t\n26\t---\n27\t\n28\t## Part 3: Screens\n29\t\n30\t### 3.1 Home (`/`)\n31\t\n32\t**Purpose:** Central dashboard showing today's snapshot — pregnancy progress, quick-log buttons, and personalized wellness nudges.\n33\t\n34\t**Scaffold:**\n35\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Baby Bump\", no back button, trailing avatar icon\n36\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Visible (4 tabs)\n37\t- `FAB`: None\n38\t\n39\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing, shows current week badge).\n40\t\n41\t**Sections:**\n42\t1. **Week Banner** — Large centered card showing pregnancy week, due date countdown, fruit-size comparison\n43\t2. **Mood Check-In Card** — Quick mood selector (5 emojis), tappable to log\n44\t3. **Today's Checklist** — Horizontal scrollable chips: weight entry, water intake, mood, symptom log\n45\t4. **Quick Actions** — 4 primary buttons: Log Weight, Log Mood, Log Symptoms, View Education\n46\t5. **Weekly Tip** — Single card with rotating wellness tip\n47\t\n48\t**Data:** Reads from `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date), `MoodEntryProvider` (today's mood), `SelfCareCheckState` (today's checklist)\n49\t\n50\t**Interactions:** Tap mood → log mood; tap weight → push weight form; tap symptom → push symptom form; tap education → tab to Education\n51\t\n52\t**Transitions:** Arrives via bottom nav tab (no animation); pull-down refreshes widget data.\n53\t\n54\t---\n55\t\n56\t### 3.2 Cycle Tracking (`/cycle-tracking`)\n57\t\n58\t**Purpose:** Log menstrual cycles, view ovulation predictions, manage cycle-related reminders.\n59\t\n60\t**Scaffold:**\n61\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Cycle Tracking\", back button\n62\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n63\t- `FAB`: `+` to log a new cycle entry\n64\t\n65\t**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n66\t\n67\t**Sections:**\n68\t1. **Current Cycle Card** — Shows days since last period, next ovulation window estimate\n69\t2. **Cycle History List** — Chronological list of logged cycles with length indicators\n70\t\n71\t**Data:** `CycleEntryProvider`\n72\t\n73\t**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet form for new cycle log; long-press history entry → edit/delete sheet; tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet\n74\t\n75\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav Browse; swipe-back to dismiss.\n76\t\n77\t---\n78\t\n79\t### 3.3 Weight & Nutrition (`/weight-nutrition`)\n80\t\n81\t**Purpose:** Log daily weight, view progress chart, read stage-specific nutrition tips.\n82\t\n83\t**Scaffold:**\n84\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Weight & Nutrition\", back button\n85\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n86\t- `FAB`: `+` to log today's weight\n87\t\n88\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n89\t\n90\t**Sections:**\n91\t1. **Progress Chart** — Line chart of weight over time; toggles 1 week / 1 month / all time\n92\t2. **Latest Entry** — Today's weight with delta from previous entry\n93\t3. **Nutrition Tips** — Stage-specific card (updates based on current pregnancy week)\n94\t4. **Weight Log List** — Scrollable list of all entries (date + weight + optional note)\n95\t\n96\t**Data:** `WeightEntryProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider` (for week-based tips)\n97\t\n98\t**Interactions:** Tap chart toggle → re-renders chart; tap `+` → bottom sheet form; long-press log entry → edit/delete sheet; tap nutrition tip → expand detail\n99\t\n100\t**Transitions:** Push from Home Browse tab or Education detail; swipe-back to dismiss.\n101\t\n102\t---\n103\t\n104\t### 3.4 Pregnancy Progress (`/pregnancy-progress`)\n105\t\n106\t**Purpose:** Due date management, week-by-week body change descriptions, fetal development visuals.\n107\t\n108\t**Scaffold:**\n109\t- `AppBar`: Title \"My Pregnancy\", back button\n110\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n111\t- `FAB`: None\n112\t\n113\t**Body:** `PageView` with `PageController` (week-by-week swiper) + bottom summary section.\n114\t\n115\t**Sections:**\n116\t1. **Week Hero** — Full-screen illustrated card with fruit-size comparison and week number prominently displayed\n117\t2. **Body Changes** — Bulleted list of what to expect this week\n118\t3. **Baby Development** — Short paragraph on fetal development\n119\t4. **Self-Care Tips** — 3 actionable tips for this week\n120\t5. **Due Date Summary** — Bottom card showing due date, days remaining, trimester badge\n121\t\n122\t**Data:** `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date)\n123\t\n124\t**Interactions:** Swipe left/right → navigate weeks; tap self-care tip → expand to full recommendation\n125\t\n126\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; PageView swipe-back returns to previous screen.\n127\t\n128\t---\n129\t\n130\t### 3.5 Mindfulness (`/mindfulness`)\n131\t\n132\t**Purpose:** Guided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, mindful activity suggestions.\n133\t\n134\t**Scaffold:**\n135\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button\n136\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n137\t- `FAB`: None\n138\t\n139\t**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n140\t\n141\t**Sections:**\n142\t1. **Breathing Exercises** — Card list with exercise name, duration, difficulty badge; tap → full-screen breathing animation overlay\n143\t2. **Stretching & Self-Care** — Card list with routine name, trimester suitability, estimated time; tap → step-by-step guide bottom sheet\n144\t\n145\t**Data:** Static exercise catalog (no provider dependency for MVP); `SelfCareCheckState` for completion tracking\n146\t\n147\t**Interactions:** Tap breathing card → overlay:breathing-exercise (full-screen animated overlay); tap stretching card → overlay:stretching-guide (bottom sheet with steps)\n148\t\n149\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav; overlay slides up from bottom.\n150\t\n151\t---\n152\t\n153\t### 3.6 Health Log (`/health-log`)\n154\t\n155\t**Purpose:** Unified timeline of all health entries — symptoms, doctor visits, reminders.\n156\t\n157\t**Scaffold:**\n158\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Health Log\", back button, trailing filter icon\n159\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n160\t- `FAB`: `+` to add new entry\n161\t\n162\t**Body:** `ListView` with chronological timeline.\n163\t\n164\t**Sections:**\n165\t1. **Timeline** — Mixed list of `SymptomEntry`, `DoctorVisit`, `Reminder` entries sorted by date descending\n166\t2. **Summary Stats** — Top banner: total symptoms logged this week, next upcoming reminder\n167\t\n168\t**Data:** `SymptomEntryProvider`, `DoctorVisitProvider`, `ReminderProvider`\n169\t\n170\t**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet with entry type selector; tap entry → detail/edit bottom sheet; tap filter icon → bottom sheet filter options\n171\t\n172\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n173\t\n174\t---\n175\t\n176\t### 3.7 Mood & Wellness (`/mood-wellness`)\n177\t\n178\t**Purpose:** Log daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over time, receive gentle wellness nudges.\n179\t\n180\t**Scaffold:**\n181\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Mood & Wellness\", back button\n182\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n183\t- `FAB`: None\n184\t\n185\t**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n186\t\n187\t**Sections:**\n188\t1. **Today's Mood Card** — Large emoji selector (5 options) + optional note field; tap to log\n189\t2. **Mood Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of mood scores; tap data point → day detail\n190\t3. **Energy Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of energy levels\n191\t4. **Wellness Tip** — Contextual recommendation based on recent mood/energy patterns\n192\t\n193\t**Data:** `MoodEntryProvider`\n194\t\n195\t**Interactions:** Tap emoji → saves mood for today; tap chart point → bottom sheet with day's detail; tap wellness tip → expand\n196\t\n197\t**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n198\t\n199\t---\n200\t\n201\t### 3.8 Education (`/education`)\n202\t\n203\t**Purpose:** Browse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic.\n204\t\n205\t**Scaffold:**\n206\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon\n207\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n208\t- `FAB`: None\n209\t\n210\t**Body:** `ListView` with topic sections.\n211\t\n212\t**Sections:**\n213\t1. **Featured Article** — Hero card at top with large image and headline\n214\t2. **Topics Grid** — 2-column grid of topic cards: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health\n215\t3. **Recent Articles** — Horizontal scroll of recently viewed articles\n216\t\n217\t**Data:** Static article catalog (no provider for MVP); `ArticleProvider` for bookmarking\n218\t\n219\t**Interactions:** Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list); tap article → `/article-reader/:id`; tap search → search overlay; tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark\n220\t\n221\t**Transitions:** Push from Home or Browse tab; swipe-back to dismiss.\n222\t\n223\t---\n224\t\n225\t### 3.9 Article Reader (`/article-reader/:id`)\n226\t\n227\t**Purpose:** Read a single article with clean typography, bookmark capability.\n228\t\n229\t**Scaffold:**\n230\t- `AppBar`: Title from article topic, back button, trailing bookmark and share icons\n231\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n232\t- `FAB`: None\n233\t\n234\t**Body:** `SingleChildScrollView` with article content.\n235\t\n236\t**Sections:**\n237\t1. **Article Header** — Hero image, topic badge, title, read-time estimate\n238\t2. **Article Body** — Formatted text with section headers, pull-quote styling\n239\t3. **Related Articles** — Bottom section with 2–3 related article cards\n240\t\n241\t**Data:** `ArticleProvider`\n242\t\n243\t**Interactions:** Tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark state; tap share → system share sheet; tap related article → push new Article Reader; scroll → collapses header image\n244\t\n245\t**Transitions:** Push from Education list or Home; shared-element hero from article card; swipe-back to dismiss.\n246\t\n247\t---\n248\t\n249\t### 3.10 Settings (`/settings`)\n250\t\n251\t**Purpose:** Manage user profile, due date, notification preferences, and data export.\n252\t\n253\t**Scaffold:**\n254\t- `AppBar`: Title \"Settings\", back button\n255\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n256\t- `FAB`: None\n257\t\n258\t**Body:** `ListView` grouped into preference sections.\n259\t\n260\t**Sections:**\n261\t1. **Profile** — Due date display with edit capability, name field\n262\t2. **Notifications** — Toggle switches for reminder categories\n263\t3. **Data** — Export data button, clear data button (with confirmation dialog)\n264\t4. **About** — App version, privacy policy link\n265\t\n266\t**Data:** `UserPreferencesProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n267\t\n268\t**Interactions:** Tap due date → date picker bottom sheet; tap export → generates shareable file; tap clear data → confirmation dialog\n269\t\n270\t**Transitions:** Push from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar; swipe-back to dismiss.\n271\t\n272\t---\n273\t\n274\t## Part 4: Navigation Architecture\n275\t\n276\t### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)\n277\t```\n278\tShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)\n279\t├── Home (/')\n280\t├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition\n281\t├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log\n282\t└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness\n283\t```\n284\t\n285\t### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)\n286\t| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |\n287\t|---|---|---|---|\n288\t| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |\n289\t| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |\n290\t| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |\n291\t| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |\n292\t\n293\t### Push Routes (detail screens)\n294\t| Screen | Route | Parent |\n295\t|---|---|---|\n296\t| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |\n297\t| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |\n298\t| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |\n299\t| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |\n300\t| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |\n301\t| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |\n302\t| Education | `/education` | Library tab |\n303\t| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |\n304\t| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |\n305\t\n306\t### Modal Overlays\n307\t| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |\n308\t|---|---|---|---|\n309\t| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |\n310\t| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |\n311\t| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |\n312\t| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |\n313\t\n314\t### Deep Links\n315\t- `babybump://home` → `/`\n316\t- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`\n317\t- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`\n318\t- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`\n319\t\n320\t---\n321\t\n322\t## Part 5: Data Context\n323\t\n324\t### Entities\n325\t\n326\t| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |\n327\t|---|---|---|---|\n328\t| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |\n329\t| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |\n330\t| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |\n331\t| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |\n332\t| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |\n333\t| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |\n334\t| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |\n335\t| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |\n336\t| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |\n337\t| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |\n338\t\n339\t### Relationships\n340\t- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)\n341\t- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts\n342\t- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard\n343\t- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab\n344\t\n345\t---\n346\t\n347\t## Part 6: Design Tokens\n348\t\n349\t### Color Palette (Material 3 — Lavender Seed)\n350\t| Token | Hex | Usage |\n351\t|---|---|---|\n352\t| `seed` | `#A78BFA` | Primary color seed (soft violet) |\n353\t| `primary` | `#7C3AED` | AppBar, FAB, primary actions |\n354\t| `secondary` | `#F9A8D4` | Blush rose accents, mood emojis |\n355\t| `tertiary` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, checkmarks |\n356\t| `surface` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n357\t| `background` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background (lavender tint) |\n358\t| `error` | `#EF4444` | Validation errors, delete actions |\n359\t| `onPrimary` | `#FFFFFF` | Text on primary color |\n360\t| `onSurface` | `#1F2937` | Body text |\n361\t| `onSurfaceVariant` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n362\t\n363\t### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n364\t| Style | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height |\n365\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n366\t| `displayLarge` | Nunito | 32sp | 700 | 40sp |\n367\t| `headlineMedium` | Nunito | 24sp | 700 | 32sp |\n368\t| `titleLarge` | Nunito | 20sp | 600 | 28sp |\n369\t| `titleMedium` | Nunito | 16sp | 600 | 24sp |\n370\t| `bodyLarge` | Nunito | 16sp | 400 | 24sp |\n371\t| `bodyMedium` | Nunito | 14sp | 400 | 20sp |\n372\t| `labelLarge` | Nunito | 14sp | 600 | 20sp |\n373\t| `caption` | Nunito | 12sp | 400 | 16sp |\n374\t\n375\t### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n376\t| Token | Value |\n377\t|---|---|\n378\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n379\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n380\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n381\t| `md` | 16dp |\n382\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n383\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n384\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n385\t\n386\t### Corner Radius Scale\n387\t| Token | Value |\n388\t|---|---|\n389\t| `sm` | 8dp (chips, small cards) |\n390\t| `md` | 12dp (cards, bottom sheets) |\n391\t| `lg` | 16dp (large cards, dialogs) |\n392\t| `full` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n393\t\n394\t### Elevation (Material 3 Tonal)\n395\t| Token | Usage |\n396\t|---|---|\n397\t| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n398\t| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n399\t| `level2` | FAB, BottomSheet |\n400\t| `level3` | Dialogs, overlays |\n401\t\n402\t### Motion\n403\t| Token | Value |\n404\t|---|---|\n405\t| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n406\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n407\t| `durationLong` | 400ms |\n408\t| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n409\t| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n410\t| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n411\t| `sharedAxis` | Hero transitions between list and detail |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2444bea1-bf77-4458-b4d2-72e2e3e7f792","uuid":"f97c2d3c-2e68-4d9e-9d63-a194cfb401ad","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:09:55.860Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/UX.md","content":"# Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump — UX Specification\n\n## Part 1: Project Overview\n\n**App Name:** Pregnant Tracker - Baby Bump\n**Platform:** Flutter Mobile (iOS & Android)\n**Core Identity:** Calming, nurturing, empowering, trustworthy\n\n### User Personas\n\n| Persona | Description | Key Goals |\n|---|---|---|\n| First-Time Expecting Mothers | First pregnancy, seeking guidance and reassurance | Week-by-week progress, trusted information, due date tracking |\n| Health-Conscious Mothers | Actively monitors weight, nutrition, exercise | Data-driven charts, daily logs, actionable insights |\n| Anxiety-Prone Mothers | Elevated stress and emotional changes | Breathing exercises, mood logging, stress relief |\n\n---\n\n## Part 2: Vibe\n\n- **Visual Atmosphere:** Soft, warm nursery aesthetic — like a cozy sunlit room with gentle natural light\n- **Color Mood:** Cool-warm pastels anchored by lavender with blush rose accents; serene, never clinical\n- **Typography Character:** Rounded, friendly, modern — Google Fonts \"Nunito\" family; generous letter-spacing for calm readability\n- **Motion Personality:** Gentle spring-based animations with `Curves.easeInOut`; 300–400ms standard duration; nothing abrupt or bouncy\n\n---\n\n## Part 3: Screens\n\n### 3.1 Home (`/`)\n\n**Purpose:** Central dashboard showing today's snapshot — pregnancy progress, quick-log buttons, and personalized wellness nudges.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Baby Bump\", no back button, trailing avatar icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Visible (4 tabs)\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar` (collapsing, shows current week badge).\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Week Banner** — Large centered card showing pregnancy week, due date countdown, fruit-size comparison\n2. **Mood Check-In Card** — Quick mood selector (5 emojis), tappable to log\n3. **Today's Checklist** — Horizontal scrollable chips: weight entry, water intake, mood, symptom log\n4. **Quick Actions** — 4 primary buttons: Log Weight, Log Mood, Log Symptoms, View Education\n5. **Weekly Tip** — Single card with rotating wellness tip\n\n**Data:** Reads from `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date), `MoodEntryProvider` (today's mood), `SelfCareCheckState` (today's checklist)\n\n**Interactions:** Tap mood → log mood; tap weight → push weight form; tap symptom → push symptom form; tap education → tab to Education\n\n**Transitions:** Arrives via bottom nav tab (no animation); pull-down refreshes widget data.\n\n---\n\n### 3.2 Cycle Tracking (`/cycle-tracking`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log menstrual cycles, view ovulation predictions, manage cycle-related reminders.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Cycle Tracking\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to log a new cycle entry\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Current Cycle Card** — Shows days since last period, next ovulation window estimate\n2. **Cycle History List** — Chronological list of logged cycles with length indicators\n\n**Data:** `CycleEntryProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet form for new cycle log; long-press history entry → edit/delete sheet; tap ovulation window → detail bottom sheet\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav Browse; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 Weight & Nutrition (`/weight-nutrition`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log daily weight, view progress chart, read stage-specific nutrition tips.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Weight & Nutrition\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to log today's weight\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Progress Chart** — Line chart of weight over time; toggles 1 week / 1 month / all time\n2. **Latest Entry** — Today's weight with delta from previous entry\n3. **Nutrition Tips** — Stage-specific card (updates based on current pregnancy week)\n4. **Weight Log List** — Scrollable list of all entries (date + weight + optional note)\n\n**Data:** `WeightEntryProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider` (for week-based tips)\n\n**Interactions:** Tap chart toggle → re-renders chart; tap `+` → bottom sheet form; long-press log entry → edit/delete sheet; tap nutrition tip → expand detail\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home Browse tab or Education detail; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.4 Pregnancy Progress (`/pregnancy-progress`)\n\n**Purpose:** Due date management, week-by-week body change descriptions, fetal development visuals.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"My Pregnancy\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `PageView` with `PageController` (week-by-week swiper) + bottom summary section.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Week Hero** — Full-screen illustrated card with fruit-size comparison and week number prominently displayed\n2. **Body Changes** — Bulleted list of what to expect this week\n3. **Baby Development** — Short paragraph on fetal development\n4. **Self-Care Tips** — 3 actionable tips for this week\n5. **Due Date Summary** — Bottom card showing due date, days remaining, trimester badge\n\n**Data:** `PregnancyProfileProvider` (current week, due date)\n\n**Interactions:** Swipe left/right → navigate weeks; tap self-care tip → expand to full recommendation\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; PageView swipe-back returns to previous screen.\n\n---\n\n### 3.5 Mindfulness (`/mindfulness`)\n\n**Purpose:** Guided breathing exercises, light stretching guides, mindful activity suggestions.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Mindfulness\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with two sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Breathing Exercises** — Card list with exercise name, duration, difficulty badge; tap → full-screen breathing animation overlay\n2. **Stretching & Self-Care** — Card list with routine name, trimester suitability, estimated time; tap → step-by-step guide bottom sheet\n\n**Data:** Static exercise catalog (no provider dependency for MVP); `SelfCareCheckState` for completion tracking\n\n**Interactions:** Tap breathing card → overlay:breathing-exercise (full-screen animated overlay); tap stretching card → overlay:stretching-guide (bottom sheet with steps)\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or bottom nav; overlay slides up from bottom.\n\n---\n\n### 3.6 Health Log (`/health-log`)\n\n**Purpose:** Unified timeline of all health entries — symptoms, doctor visits, reminders.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Health Log\", back button, trailing filter icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: `+` to add new entry\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with chronological timeline.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Timeline** — Mixed list of `SymptomEntry`, `DoctorVisit`, `Reminder` entries sorted by date descending\n2. **Summary Stats** — Top banner: total symptoms logged this week, next upcoming reminder\n\n**Data:** `SymptomEntryProvider`, `DoctorVisitProvider`, `ReminderProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap `+` FAB → bottom sheet with entry type selector; tap entry → detail/edit bottom sheet; tap filter icon → bottom sheet filter options\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.7 Mood & Wellness (`/mood-wellness`)\n\n**Purpose:** Log daily moods and energy levels, visualize patterns over time, receive gentle wellness nudges.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Mood & Wellness\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `CustomScrollView` with `SliverAppBar`.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Today's Mood Card** — Large emoji selector (5 options) + optional note field; tap to log\n2. **Mood Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of mood scores; tap data point → day detail\n3. **Energy Trend Chart** — 7-day line chart of energy levels\n4. **Wellness Tip** — Contextual recommendation based on recent mood/energy patterns\n\n**Data:** `MoodEntryProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap emoji → saves mood for today; tap chart point → bottom sheet with day's detail; tap wellness tip → expand\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.8 Education (`/education`)\n\n**Purpose:** Browse and read trusted educational articles organized by topic.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Education\", back button, trailing search icon\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` with topic sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Featured Article** — Hero card at top with large image and headline\n2. **Topics Grid** — 2-column grid of topic cards: Nutrition, Body Changes, Maternal Care, Exercise, Mental Health\n3. **Recent Articles** — Horizontal scroll of recently viewed articles\n\n**Data:** Static article catalog (no provider for MVP); `ArticleProvider` for bookmarking\n\n**Interactions:** Tap topic card → `/education/:topic` (filtered article list); tap article → `/article-reader/:id`; tap search → search overlay; tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Home or Browse tab; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.9 Article Reader (`/article-reader/:id`)\n\n**Purpose:** Read a single article with clean typography, bookmark capability.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title from article topic, back button, trailing bookmark and share icons\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `SingleChildScrollView` with article content.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Article Header** — Hero image, topic badge, title, read-time estimate\n2. **Article Body** — Formatted text with section headers, pull-quote styling\n3. **Related Articles** — Bottom section with 2–3 related article cards\n\n**Data:** `ArticleProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap bookmark icon → toggle bookmark state; tap share → system share sheet; tap related article → push new Article Reader; scroll → collapses header image\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Education list or Home; shared-element hero from article card; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n### 3.10 Settings (`/settings`)\n\n**Purpose:** Manage user profile, due date, notification preferences, and data export.\n\n**Scaffold:**\n- `AppBar`: Title \"Settings\", back button\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: Hidden\n- `FAB`: None\n\n**Body:** `ListView` grouped into preference sections.\n\n**Sections:**\n1. **Profile** — Due date display with edit capability, name field\n2. **Notifications** — Toggle switches for reminder categories\n3. **Data** — Export data button, clear data button (with confirmation dialog)\n4. **About** — App version, privacy policy link\n\n**Data:** `UserPreferencesProvider`, `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n\n**Interactions:** Tap due date → date picker bottom sheet; tap export → generates shareable file; tap clear data → confirmation dialog\n\n**Transitions:** Push from Profile tab or Settings icon in Home AppBar; swipe-back to dismiss.\n\n---\n\n## Part 4: Navigation Architecture\n\n### Navigator Structure (GoRouter)\n```\nShellRoute (BottomNavigationBar)\n├── Home (/')\n├── Browse (/browse)         ← contains Cycle Tracking, Weight & Nutrition\n├── Library (/library)       ← contains Education, Health Log\n└── Profile (/profile)      ← contains Settings, Mindfulness\n```\n\n### Bottom Navigation (4 tabs)\n| Tab | Label | Icon | Route |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Home | Home | `Icons.home_outlined` | `/` |\n| Browse | Browse | `Icons.search_outlined` | `/browse` |\n| Library | Library | `Icons.bookmark_outline` | `/library` |\n| Profile | Profile | `Icons.person_outline` | `/profile` |\n\n### Push Routes (detail screens)\n| Screen | Route | Parent |\n|---|---|---|\n| Cycle Tracking | `/cycle-tracking` | Browse tab |\n| Weight & Nutrition | `/weight-nutrition` | Browse tab |\n| Pregnancy Progress | `/pregnancy-progress` | Home tab |\n| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Profile tab |\n| Health Log | `/health-log` | Library tab |\n| Mood & Wellness | `/mood-wellness` | Library tab |\n| Education | `/education` | Library tab |\n| Article Reader | `/article-reader/:id` | Education |\n| Settings | `/settings` | Profile tab |\n\n### Modal Overlays\n| Overlay | Route | Type | Parent Screen |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Breathing Exercise | `overlay:breathing-exercise` | full-sheet overlay | Mindfulness |\n| Stretching Guide | `overlay:stretching-guide` | bottom-sheet | Mindfulness |\n| Mode Selector | `overlay:mode-selector` | bottom-sheet | Home |\n| Symptom Detail | `overlay:symptom-detail` | bottom-sheet | Health Log |\n\n### Deep Links\n- `babybump://home` → `/`\n- `babybump://browse` → `/browse`\n- `babybump://education/:id` → `/article-reader/:id`\n- `babybump://settings` → `/settings`\n\n---\n\n## Part 5: Data Context\n\n### Entities\n\n| Entity | Key Fields | Provider | Screens |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `PregnancyProfile` | dueDate, lastPeriodDate, currentWeek | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | Home, Pregnancy Progress, Settings |\n| `CycleEntry` | startDate, endDate, notes, isIrregular | `CycleEntryProvider` | Cycle Tracking |\n| `WeightEntry` | date, weightKg, note | `WeightEntryProvider` | Weight & Nutrition |\n| `MoodEntry` | date, moodScore (1-5), note, energyLevel | `MoodEntryProvider` | Home, Mood & Wellness |\n| `SymptomEntry` | date, symptomType, severity (1-3), notes | `SymptomEntryProvider` | Health Log |\n| `DoctorVisit` | date, doctorName, notes, nextVisitDate | `DoctorVisitProvider` | Health Log |\n| `Reminder` | title, date, category, isEnabled | `ReminderProvider` | Health Log |\n| `SelfCareCheckState` | date, checkedItems: List<String> | `SelfCareCheckStateProvider` | Home, Mindfulness |\n| `Article` | id, title, topic, content, imageUrl, isBookmarked | `ArticleProvider` | Education, Article Reader |\n| `UserPreferences` | name, notificationsEnabled, dueDate | `UserPreferencesProvider` | Settings |\n\n### Relationships\n- `PregnancyProfile.currentWeek` drives all week-based content (tips, body changes, nutrition advice)\n- `MoodEntryProvider` aggregates mood data for `MoodWellnessScreen` trend charts\n- `SelfCareCheckState` stores today's checklist state, consumed by Home dashboard\n- `ArticleProvider` tracks bookmarks, consumed by Library tab\n\n---\n\n## Part 6: Design Tokens\n\n### Color Palette (Material 3 — Lavender Seed)\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `seed` | `#A78BFA` | Primary color seed (soft violet) |\n| `primary` | `#7C3AED` | AppBar, FAB, primary actions |\n| `secondary` | `#F9A8D4` | Blush rose accents, mood emojis |\n| `tertiary` | `#6EE7B7` | Success states, checkmarks |\n| `surface` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `background` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background (lavender tint) |\n| `error` | `#EF4444` | Validation errors, delete actions |\n| `onPrimary` | `#FFFFFF` | Text on primary color |\n| `onSurface` | `#1F2937` | Body text |\n| `onSurfaceVariant` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, captions |\n\n### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n| Style | Font | Size | Weight | Line Height |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | Nunito | 32sp | 700 | 40sp |\n| `headlineMedium` | Nunito | 24sp | 700 | 32sp |\n| `titleLarge` | Nunito | 20sp | 600 | 28sp |\n| `titleMedium` | Nunito | 16sp | 600 | 24sp |\n| `bodyLarge` | Nunito | 16sp | 400 | 24sp |\n| `bodyMedium` | Nunito | 14sp | 400 | 20sp |\n| `labelLarge` | Nunito | 14sp | 600 | 20sp |\n| `caption` | Nunito | 12sp | 400 | 16sp |\n\n### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius Scale\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp (chips, small cards) |\n| `md` | 12dp (cards, bottom sheets) |\n| `lg` | 16dp (large cards, dialogs) |\n| `full` | 999dp (pills, avatars) |\n\n### Elevation (Material 3 Tonal)\n| Token | Usage |\n|---|---|\n| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n| `level2` | FAB, BottomSheet |\n| `level3` | Dialogs, overlays |\n\n### Motion\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms |\n| `durationLong` | 400ms |\n| `easingStandard` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| `easingEnter` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `easingExit` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n| `sharedAxis` | Hero transitions between list and detail |","numLines":411,"startLine":1,"totalLines":411}}}
